 – 澳大利亚布里斯班 – 毅力音乐厅</strong></p><p><strong>行进<br /></strong><strong>04 – 澳大利亚悉尼 – 恩莫尔剧院<br /></strong><strong>07 – 澳大利亚墨尔本 – 木材场<br /></strong><strong>08 – 澳大利亚弗里曼特尔 – 弗里曼特尔大都会</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jpegmafia-announces-uk-ireland-australia-2025-tour-tickets-3772186">JPEGMAFIA 宣布英国、爱尔兰和澳大利亚世界巡演日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
观看 Foster The People 混搭 Dua Lipa 和 Eminem 的单曲《Houdini》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-foster-the-people-mash-up-dua-lipa-and-eminems-houdini-singles-3772193?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-foster-人民混搭杜阿·利帕和阿姆·胡迪尼单曲Poppy BurtonThu, 04 Jul 2024 20:44:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3772193 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿姆和杜阿·利帕" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们在混音中解决了这个问题”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-foster-the-people-mash-up-dua-lipa-and-eminems-houdini-singles-3772193">《Watch Foster The People》之后，杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 和埃米纳姆 (Eminem) 的单曲《Houdini》的混搭</a>作品首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿姆和杜阿·利帕" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/eminem-dua-lipa-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foster-the-people">Foster the People</a>发布了一个混音版，被戏称为“胡迪尼斯之战”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/dua-lipa-live-at-glastonbury-2024-review-setlist-photos-3770003"><b>杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 的现场演出：精彩的表演让批评家闭嘴</b></a></li></ul><p>这支加州乐队在 2011 年的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-foster-the-people-12163-311918">Torches</a> ”中发行了他们的“Houdini”。几年后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a>效仿，发行了自己的歌曲，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">《激进乐观》</a>的主打单曲同名。</p><p>阿姆现在是最新加入这一行动的人，并于五月发行了他的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-references-megan-thee-stallion-shooting-incident-on-new-song-houdini-3761145">Houdini</a> ”，以纪念他即将发行的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-announces-new-album-the-death-of-slim-shady-coup-de-grace-3750971">“The Death of Slim Shady (Coup de Grâce)”</a> 。</p><p>现在，正如在社交媒体上分享的一篇文章中所看到的，Foster the People 分享了他们对这三张专辑的混音，并在标题中引用了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>并开玩笑说：“（我们在混音中解决了这个问题）”，以此向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-girl-so-confusing-remix-with-lorde-3767420">“女孩，与洛德的混音真是令人困惑</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C84-3QhuNpF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 